###register user
POST http://localhost:5000/api/common/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "Subhash_Kumar",
    "email": "subhashkumar@gmail.com",
    "password": "12345678"
}

###login user
POST http://localhost:5000/api/common/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "subhashkumar@gmail.com",
    "password": "12345678"
}

###get authenticated user
GET http://localhost:5000/api/common/user
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpZCI6IjY5YjkxMDQ3MGRhNjY2YjJhMmIwNTJmOCIsImlhdCI6MTc3MzczNjAxNCwiZXhwIjoxNzczODIyNDE0fQ.yxZKC_tw9Y8RGUvkp_ch7uTAx0LR5dfsEYH_XeGm2Wk

###logout user
POST http://localhost:5000/api/common/logout
Content-Type: application/json

